max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Bodunuz.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I have osmosed enough of TCW to know this is funny (please don't tell me to watch it, I'm not going to, the animation style is ugly as hell and there's like nine million hours of it, I can't make myself look at something I don't like looking at for that long)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SX1ekxP.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sometimes the lil pet is just another party member, and that's fine too.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/phRPy4w.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/33fuiTN.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uMs5FpQ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/by9fn5n.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I worked in a call center for a decade, this happened a LOT</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1BfgZUR.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OruziE9.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QUNz0mq.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZHTHujT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Saw the meme text on a different canon and knew what I had to do...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qb67YBk.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>GNU uncle Pete</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1oUc2Eo.png" style